Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.95,0:00:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为今天要去看军械库的其余地方呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I thought we were going to look at the rest of the armory today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.75,0:00:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果现在是今天的话\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}If it is, in fact, today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.79,0:00:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浩隆不适应早上\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Taka isn't good at mornings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.79,0:00:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且现在比早上还早\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And this is some extra morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.54,0:00:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太早了 还是昨天呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It is so much morning that it's actually still yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.00,0:00:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不该熬夜探索城堡的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, you shouldn't have stayed up so late exploring the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.66,0:00:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们想看移动城堡的引擎\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We wanted to see the engine that moved the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.54,0:00:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能修好吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Can it ever be fixed?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:00:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那需要很长时间 而我们还有别的事要做\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But it will take a very long time, and there are other things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.33,0:00:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.08,0:01:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么事比那更重要\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What could be more important than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太多了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哪都不去 浩隆\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm not going anywhere, Taka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城堡已经完成了最后一次移动\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The castle's moved for the last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.12,0:01:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一些地方我需要守卫\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I have places to guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔法灯笼\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Magic lanterns!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.04,0:02:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是闪电 不是魔法\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Lightning. Not magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把闪电装进灯笼里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You put lightning into lamps
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还说不是魔法\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and you tell us it's not magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的不是\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's really not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.45,0:02:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早在公元前两百年 帕提亚人就把闪电存进了罐子里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The Parthians were storing lightning in jars two hundred years before Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是贝尔蒙特密室\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This is the Belmont Hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个家族的最终存储库\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The final repository of a family
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们世世代代只学习如何做一件事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}who spent generations learning how to do one thing:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.41,0:02:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀怪物\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Kill monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包括吸血鬼\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Including vampires.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:03:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们想学关于杀吸血鬼的所有知识\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You want to learn everything about killing vampires?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.79,0:03:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是贝尔蒙特家族的毕生研究\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The Belmonts made it their lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且都写下来了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and they wrote it all down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们了解吸血鬼解剖结构吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Do you understand the anatomy of a vampire?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用尖锐的东西刺入他们心脏\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You put a stabby thing into their heart
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们就灰飞烟灭\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and they go boom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比这要复杂一点\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's a little more complicated than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但算一个好开头\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Good start, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.79,0:03:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...人呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What about... people?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你们知道怎么杀人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm fairly sure you know how to kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.75,0:03:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿町有许多人类战奴\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Cho had many human warrior slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许我们根本应付不过来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Maybe more than we can take on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以看看战术\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, we can look at tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.41,0:03:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有闪电灯笼呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And the lightning lamps.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闪电也能做武器吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Can lightning be a weapon, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.83,0:03:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能用闪电一下子杀死很多人吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Could you make lightning kill a lot of people at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从小事做起 好吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Let's start small, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.83,0:03:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然 我们只是担心很多事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Of course. We are just worried about a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直很善良 我们无比感恩\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You're being incredibly kind, and we are very grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你们担心\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I know you're worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.25,0:03:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浩隆 你必须明白\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Taka, you need to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不只是在传授杀人的方法\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}that I'm not just passing on ways to murder people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是我们的处境十分不利\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's just that the odds are so stacked against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我夜不能寐\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I can't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才整夜在城堡里走来走去\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That's why I was wandering around the castle all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.54,0:04:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,珠美只是为了陪我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sumi was just keeping me company.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 好吧 但是…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All right, all right. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们必须明白\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}you do need to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你们分享这些信息\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm sharing all of this with you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为的是让你们记住并传承下去\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}so that you'll remember it and pass it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只是战争部分的内容\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Not just the war-making.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是全部\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得特雷弗·贝尔蒙特会喜欢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I think Trevor Belmont would like the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武装新一代怪物猎人的点子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}of equipping a new generation of monster hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准跑\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No running!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说过无数次了 我不准孩子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I've told you a thousand times I won't have children
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像野狗一样在我的镇上到处乱窜\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}running like wild dogs through my town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是你 我最少说了20次 不是吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And I've told you, in particular, more than twenty times, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是 孩子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Haven't I, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.54,0:05:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一大早过来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And you're here first thing in the morning
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你喜欢最新鲜的苹果 是吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}because you like the freshest apples, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我猜也是\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Mmm. I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想知道一个秘密吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Would you like to know a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你穿过后方的空地进入树林\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}If you go into the woods through the back field
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并沿着小路走到岔口\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and follow the path until the fork,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,选择有棵大树的那条路 就是你们都说它像一张愤怒的脸的那棵\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and you go down the way with the big tree that you all say looks like an angry face,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后淌过小溪\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and you go over the creek,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经过你父母说不该去的那地方...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}past the point the way your parents say you shouldn't go...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.29,0:05:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我恰好知道 在那后面的空地上有一棵苹果树\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I happen to know there's an apple tree in the clearing after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,树是我的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's my apple tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不允许去那里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and nobody's allowed to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 如果你保证不告诉任何人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So, if you promise not to tell a soul where you're going...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能去摘三个苹果\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Go and get yourself three apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有 不准再跑了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And no more running.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你起得真早\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You're up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要做的事情太多 可能来不及\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Lots to do. Probably not enough time to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:06:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说你昨天跟贝尔纳德斯和贝尔蒙特喝酒了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm told you were drinking with Belnades and Belmont yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是大名人 而且他们想看看见过厕纸的人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am extremely famous and they wanted to meet someone who'd seen toilet paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.95,0:06:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厕纸是什么鬼东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What the fuck is toilet paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中国特产 早上好 法官\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's Chinese. Good morning, Judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厕纸\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Toilet paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是应该出现在修道院的东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Not an obvious thing to find in a church.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉院长\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Uh, Prior Sala?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉院长\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Prior Sala!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 圣日耳曼\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, good. Saint Germain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有个问题 院长\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}A question, Prior.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕我们今早很忙\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We are quite busy this morning, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这本书 你认识吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Th-This book. Do you recognize it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不认识\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.95,0:08:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为修道院出现这本书很不寻常\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Because it's an unusual book to find in a church.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,众所周知 老院长们藏过一些\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Old priories are known to find themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不同寻常的古书\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}storing old and unusual books.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Indeed so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但有人在最近看过这本书 萨拉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But someone recently read this book, Sala.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后撕掉了其中一段\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}After which they tore a section out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多书都有损毁\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Many of these books are damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白你为何如此激动\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't see why this should excite you so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为撕痕尚未变黄 萨拉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Because the tears haven't yellowed, Sala.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一段是在过去几个月里撕掉的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The section was removed within the last few months.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,边缘的烟灰还没散 而且…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The soot on the edges is still loose. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.79,0:08:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁从你的收藏中选了这本书\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}who selected this book from your collection?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看不出来我为什么应该对这本书感兴趣\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I fail to see why this should interest me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为撕掉的那段记载着让人从地狱…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Because the missing section involves methods and processes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.37,0:08:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,归来的方法和过程\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}for returning people from Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许有人只是单纯地撕掉那几页\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Perhaps someone simply pulled out those pages
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.37,0:08:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用来擦屁股了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to wipe their backside with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道东方人用纸擦屁股\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I understand they use paper for that in the Orient.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这本书是由两百年前一位锻造师写的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This book was written by a forgemaster some two hundred years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一位不走寻常路的疯狂锻造师\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}an insane forgemaster who did not practice in the usual way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有任何德古拉的信息吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Is there any mention of Dracula?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有 但这不是重点...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No. But you miss the point...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.83,0:09:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你最好回去工作\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Then you had better get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sala.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你曾让我不要把你当成疯子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You told me not to treat you as if you were mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让我失望\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Do not disappoint me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.91,0:10:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 锻造师先生\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Good morning, Sir Forgemaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认识我吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我闻到你的气味了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I smell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.75,0:10:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会发现 这里没有鲜活的肉体供你杀害和锻造\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You'll find no fresh bodies to kill and forge here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.66,0:10:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里就你一个人吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You're alone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全没错\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个人的村子可不多见\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's not every day you see a one-person village.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前 这里曾经人满为患\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Once upon a time, you may have found it quite over-full.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十人住一栋房子 到处是吵嚷的孩子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Ten people to a house. Screaming kids everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太拥挤了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It was teeming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说真的 有时候我觉得这样更好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Honestly? Sometimes I like it a little better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你干的吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Did you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 天啊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, no. Oh, God, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全超出了我的能力\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Quite outside my powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前面50公里处有一个镇子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There's a town thirty miles up the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.33,0:11:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里更像个监狱\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}more of a prison, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然那是我要去的方向\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Since that is the direction I'm headed,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许你能给一个旅行者和同修\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}perhaps you'd give a traveler and fellow practitioner
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个善意的警告\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}a friendly warning?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也能闻出我的气味吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You can smell me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能看出来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:12:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,镇子被一个魔法师控制着\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The town is run by a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他梦想用奴隶\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He has dreams of a city,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建造一座城市\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}a slave population to build it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以他扫荡了周围的村庄\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So he swept up the surrounding villages,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他们的灵魂烧成灰烬\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}cooked their souls down to ash...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他们变成了蝼蚁\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}turned them into ants.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他们吃屎\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Make them eat shit
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.54,0:12:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和搬砖\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and stack bricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...你还在这\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But... you're still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.33,0:12:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你任由这个魔法师抓走了你的邻居\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So, you let this magician take your neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道为什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 除非你根本不是你假装出来的样子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Unless, of course, you're not quite what you pass yourself off as.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我..就是\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh... I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是没有以前那么强大了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm just not as strong as I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种生活要付出代价 锻造师\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This life takes a toll, Forgemaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It does.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫艾萨克\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am Isaac.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.87,0:13:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米兰达\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Miranda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能自保 但是…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You were able to protect yourself, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能把他们从我身边吓跑\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I was able to frighten them away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但魔法力量已经很弱了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But the magic is thin now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我无法帮助任何人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I couldn't do a thing for anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只能眼睁睁看着\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I had to just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个魔法师没回来找你吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The magician never came back for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他没有理由回来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He has no reason to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在也能自保\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I can still defend myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他没办法转化我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}he wouldn't be able to turn me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对他来说有多少价值呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And how much use would I be to him, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他已经有了所需要的一切\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He has what he needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个狗日的疯子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The mad bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里建一个城邦\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Building a city-state here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天 施第里尔人会冲进围绕他的城市\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}One day the Styrians will punch through the cities that enclose them
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蜂拥到全国各地\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and swarm across the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去施第里尔\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm going to Styria.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.20,0:14:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 为什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Why, for God's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里有我要杀的人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I have people to kill there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你需要更多黑暗生物\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, you will need more of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.16,0:14:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且骑马还要两星期才能到\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And Styria is still a good two weeks' ride from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被人背叛了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I was betrayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对此无能为力\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I could not do a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说的魔法师\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The magician I spoke of
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一面传送镜 艾萨克\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}has a transmission mirror, Isaac.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:15:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个非常高非常宽的镜子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}One that is unusually tall and wide,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一次能传送很多人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and can transmit many people at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 想获得那样的宝贝\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Of course, to obtain such a treasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得杀光镇上所有人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}you will have to kill everyone in that town,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让魔法师失去防卫\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}so that the magician has no defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从而将所有人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Thereby converting the entire population
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,转化为更多的黑暗生物\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}into more of your night creatures,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为你装备一支完整的军队\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}equipping you with a full army
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.37,0:15:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去施第里尔复仇\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to take your revenge in Styria.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我早该告诉你 我非常生气\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes, I probably should have mentioned that I am quite mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀光他们吧 帅气的锻造师\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, kill them all, pretty forgemaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.62,0:15:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会为此感谢你的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They'll thank you for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且他们会感谢你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And they'll thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他们变成了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}for turning them into instruments of revenge
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.16,0:15:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向人类复仇的工具\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}against the human race.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:16:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去救我的老邻居吧 然后夺取你的战利品\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Go and save my old neighbors, and take your reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那会让一位疲惫不堪的老同修高兴不已\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It would please a tired old colleague in your art,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是那才是正义\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and it would be justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.54,0:16:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这世上有比施第里尔的吸血鬼\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There are worse things in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更糟的东西 艾萨克\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}than vampires in Styria, Isaac.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有比背叛...更糟的东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There are worse things... than betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:16:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓到他们了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Got them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在怎么办\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们去质问他们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I suppose we question them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只需要其中一个就够了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We only need one of them for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们不想惊动修道院\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And we don't need the alarm raised in the priory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么建议吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Do you have a suggestion?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交给我处理吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Let me take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自从这件事与魔法和奇怪的符号扯上关系\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I've felt bloody useless ever since all of this
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就觉得自己很没用\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}became about magic and weird symbology.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.20,0:17:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你确定吗  -确定\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- Are you sure? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.29,0:17:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是个容易满足的简单男人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm a simple man with simple pleasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的喜欢遇到职业杀手\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, I do like meeting a professional killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种握法 每次都能暴露身份\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And that grip gives it away every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找到故意破坏公物的人了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I've found your vandal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一个很淘气的修道士\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He's a very naughty monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们抓到他在一栋房子一侧刻一个符号\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We caught him carving a symbol into the side of a home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我们在前门看到的那个符号\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The one we saw at the front gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在村子各处都能看到那个符号\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The one seen in a few places around the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.83,0:20:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个符号带着令人不安的含义\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}One with a troubling set of meanings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.12,0:20:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉法官那个符号代表什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Tell the Judge what the symbol means.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.08,0:20:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Fuck you to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.75,0:20:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我说话的时候放尊重点 修道士\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Keep a civil fucking tongue in your head when you're addressing me, monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不会说\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm telling you nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不能把我关在这 你们屁都做不了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You can't keep me here. You can't do a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.83,0:20:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以直接杀了你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We could just kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.41,0:21:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信我居然试着对你客气\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I can't believe I tried to be nice to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个符号有一组含义 合起来就是\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The symbol has a set of meanings that, taken together,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"死亡和转化"\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}mean death and transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在谋划一些魔法本质的事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They're planning something magical in nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得这是个计划吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And you think this is a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉和他的修道士\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sala and his people are intending
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.66,0:21:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算对这个镇子采取某种行动\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to take some kind of action against the town?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.25,0:21:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以确定\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm certain of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 告诉我具体是什么行动\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, tell me exactly what action.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是很清楚\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I do not exactly know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他很清楚\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.33,0:21:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有 圣日耳曼在修道院里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And Saint Germain is inside the priory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚他知道了我们的怀疑\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He shared our suspicions last night.
